            </li>
            <li id="sex-gender-tab">
                <h2>Sexual Activity by Gender</h2>
                <div id="sex-gender" class="graph"></div>
                <p>Men were more likely than women to report having lost their virginity. Moreover, men were likely to have had sex at a younger age than women.</p>
            </li>
            <li id="sex-age-tab">
                <h2>Age of First Sexual Activity Among Non-Virgins</h2>
