            </li>
            <li id="sex-partners-tab">
                <h2>Sexual Partners</h2>
                <div id="sex-partners" class="graph"></div>
                <p>The majority of those who have had sex&mdash;62 percent&mdash;said they&#39;ve only done the deed with one person. Seven respondents, all of whom were male, reported having had sex with more than 10 partners.</p>
            </li>
            <li id="sex-religion-tab">
                <h2>Sexual Activity by Religion</h2>
                <div id="sex-religion" class="graph"></div>
